<link href="/css/bootstrap/carousel.css" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
    .custom-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        min-width: 120px;
        height: 40px;
        padding: 0 23px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 38px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        text-align: center;
        -webkit-transition: background-color .1s linear,border-color .1s linear;
        -moz-transition: background-color .1s linear,border-color .1s linear;
        transition: background-color .1s linear,border-color .1s linear;
        color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #000;
        background-color: #000;
    }
</style>
{{>layout/header}}

<!--헤더 시작-->
<header>
    <!--네비게이션 바-->
    <nav class="navbar fixed-top navbar-expand-lg navbar-light" style="background-color: white; border-bottom: 1px solid #CCCCCC;">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><img src="/images/tistory_icon_black.png" height="30" width="30"></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                    <li class="nav-item" style="width: 50px;">
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="#" style="font-weight: 900; font-size: 12pt;">피드</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item" style="width: 30px;">
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="#" style="font-weight: 900; font-size: 12pt;">스토리</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <button class="custom-btn" onclick="location.href='/auth/login'">시작하기</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
</header>
<!--헤더 끝-->

<!--메인 시작-->
<main>
    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <svg class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"></rect></svg>

                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption text-start">
                        <h1>당신의 이야기가 값진 수익이 됩니다.</h1>
                        <p>심사부터 광고 설정, 수익 확인까지 티스토리에서 바로 할 수 있어요</p>
                        <p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="#">Sign up today</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <svg class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"></rect></svg>

                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h1>티스토리 앱 2.0 업데이트</h1>
                        <p>모바일에서도 편리한 블로그 관리를 위해 티스토리 앱이 새 옷을 입었습니다.</p>
                        <p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="#">Learn more</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <svg class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"></rect></svg>

                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption text-end">
                        <h1>이제부터 티스토리를 카카오계정으로 이용해주세요.</h1>
                        <p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="#">Browse gallery</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>


